{"data":[{"id":562733426,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"dc3cb7a6b1e2bb51c1e939d29b2ca430","url_token":"bai-san-71","name":"小池一别","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2ef7cec86525d37ea26a84ecd0ca022c_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2ef7cec86525d37ea26a84ecd0ca022c_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/dc3cb7a6b1e2bb51c1e939d29b2ca430","user_type":"people","headline":"「杨超越挑战赛发起者，详见想法」","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":254,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562733426","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546140125,"updated_time":1546141003,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e对，高中生解出哥猜是万无可能的。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e所以，在这个问题下嘲讽题主是绝对安全的。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e是吗？\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主呢，不管他是哗众取宠也好，真的不自量力也好，至少他的语言还算平和，对各位明显带有嘲讽和蔑视的评论我看他并不怎么回击。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我姑且认为这是一个有些理智的人。（说实话，比一部分答题的人更理智）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主其实讲的很明白：他不确定自己一定证对了，但他“证明出来了”。那么他其实就是到知乎上征求一些意见。对嘲讽简单回复一下，然后默默收藏有价值的回复（对，他竟然真的在记那些邮箱和电话）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而这个问题下的很多答主，怎么说呢？就仿佛知乎盛产的一类人，其实他也不是内行，但是他们不会放过任何一个安全的出言嘲讽的机会。就像现在，一个高中生不自量力的证明哥猜，万无可能，所以可以开始嘲了，绝对安全。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可是确实如此吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当嘲讽成为习惯，总有一天你会踩中真东西，总有一天万无可能之事会在“万”外发生。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e甚至这个表面上高中生的题主，谁又知道他是不是某个研究群体意识的学者呢？也许他专门为了研究“哗众取宠”，以及“所有人都踩了一脚我也来踩一脚”这种事呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然了，嘲讽被打脸是最微不足道的事了，毕竟嘲讽的快乐是敲敲键盘就能得到了。而讽刺力的回馈隔着网线反不到大家的现实生活中嘛。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后回到问题，我是不信题主能证出来的，但是如果你真证对了，我为你鼓掌。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"\u003cb\u003e对，高中生解出哥猜是万无可能的。\u003c/b\u003e\u003cb\u003e所以，在这个问题下嘲讽题主是绝对安全的。\u003c/b\u003e \u003cb\u003e是吗？\u003c/b\u003e 题主呢，不管他是哗众取宠也好，真的不自量力也好，至少他的语言还算平和，对各位明显带有嘲讽和蔑视的评论我看他并不怎么回击。我姑且认为这是一个有些理智的人。（说实…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.